import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Nav } from 'grommet'

const NavBar = (props) => (
  <nav>
    <Nav>
      <Link to="/graph">Graph</Link>
    </Nav>
  </nav>
)

export default NavBar
